Scenario
HMCTS requires a new system to be developed so caseworkers can keep track of their tasks.
Your technical test is to develop that new system so caseworkers can efficiently manage their tasks.


Task Requirements
Backend API
The backend should be able to:

Create a task with the following properties:
Title
Description (optional field)
Status
Due date/time
Retrieve a task by ID
Retrieve all tasks
Update the status of a task
Delete a task
Frontend Application
The frontend should be able to:

Create, view, update, and delete tasks
Display tasks in a user-friendly interface